com.linkedin.cubert.operator.cube

Class EasyCubeAggregatorBridge

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.linkedin.cubert.operator.cube.EasyCubeAggregatorBridge
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CubeAggregator, DupleCubeAggregator

    public class EasyCubeAggregatorBridge
extends Object
implements DupleCubeAggregator
    A bridge class that wraps user-defined aggregation functions (UDAFs) written with EasyCubeAggregator interface into DupleCubeAggregator interface.
